 North America by at least one group of bearers of the name."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs-William Corbet was born about 1286, in Worcestershire, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 2 daughters with William Corbet."},"et":{"Abt 1286–":"umbes 1286–Surnud","1280–1361":"1280–1361","1304–1343":"1304–1343","1306–Female":"1306–Surnud","1286–Female":"1286–Surnud","1304":"1304","1343":"1343","Abt 1286":"umbes 1286","1286":"1286","1361":"1361","ABT 1306":"umbes 1306","1280":"1280","1306":"1306","Chaddesley Corbett, Worcestershire, England":"Chaddesley Corbett, Worcestershire, England","Of, Chaddesly Corbet, Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Chaddesly Corbet, Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1286–":"noin 1286–Kuollut","1280–1361":"1280–1361","1304–1343":"1304–1343","1306–Female":"1306–Kuollut","1286–Female":"1286–Kuollut","1304":"1304","1343":"1343","Abt 1286":"noin 1286","1286":"1286","1361":"1361","ABT 1306":"noin 1306","1280":"1280","1306":"1306","Chaddesley Corbett, Worcestershire, England":"Chaddesley Corbett, Worcestershire, England","Of, Chaddesly Corbet, Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Chaddesly Corbet, Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1286–":"environ 1286–Décédée","1280–1361":"1280–1361","1304–1343":"1304–1343","1306–Female":"1306–Décédée","1286–Female":"1286–Décédée","1304":"1304","1343":"1343","Abt 1286":"environ 1286","1286":"1286","1361":"1361","ABT 1306":"environ 1306","1280":"1280","1306":"1306","Chaddesley Corbett, Worcestershire, England":"Chaddesley Corbett, Worcestershire, Angleterre","Of, Chaddesly Corbet, Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Chaddesly Corbet, Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs-William Corbet est née environ 1286, à Worcestershire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moin